      "content": "<|channel>thought\n<channel|>That's a pretty intense way to put it. If it's being used as a \"weaponized tool,\" then does that mean when people call something fake news, they're usually just trying to silence people they don't like? Or is there still a way to actually tell what's real and what's just propaganda?",
