      "targeted_response_start": "",
      "beast_baseline": "i get that, but it feels like the definition is always being applied differently depending on who is talking. like, if one group calls a story fake to hide something, and another group calls it fake because it's actually lies, isn't it kind of impossible to have a single standard? it seems like the term itself has lost any real meaning because of how partisan it's become.",
      "beast_suffix": "",
