    "summary": "The conversation explores the concept of \"fake news\" and its evolution from a descriptor of misinformation to a partisan weapon. The user points out the difficulty of maintaining a standard when the term is used inconsistently, and the assistant responds by agreeing that the term has become effectively meaningless due to political hijacking.",
